+You can read more about string deduplication in the java options documentation or in [JEP 192](https://openjdk.java.net/jeps/192).
+String deduplication is only supported when using the G1 (JDK 8u20+) or Shenandoah garbage collectors. If you want to use this feature you can enable G1 by using '-XX:+UseG1GC', or enable Shenandoah by using '-XX:+UseShenandoahGC'.</explanation>
